<inglise> COMMISSION DECISION of 2 May 1988 on the eligibility of expenditure for the development of monitoring and supervision facilities necessary for applying the Community arrangements for the conservation of fishery resources </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI OTSUS kulutuste abik&otilde;lblikkuse kohta seire- ja kontrollivahendite arendamiseks, mis on vajalikud &uuml;henduse korra rakendamisel kalavarude kaitseks 2. mai 1988 </eesti>
<inglise> (Only the Danish, French, English, Dutch, Portuguese and Spanish texts are authentic) </inglise>
<eesti> (Ainult taani-, prantsus-, inglis-, hollandi-, portugali- ja hispaaniakeelne tekst on autentne) </eesti>
<inglise> (88/307/EEC) </inglise>
<eesti> (88/307/EM&Uuml;) </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Decision 87/278/EEC of 18 May 1987 on Community financial contribution to the development of the monitoring and supervision facilities necessary for applying the Community arrangements for the conservation of fishery resources (1), and in particular paragraph 4 of the Annex thereto, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 18. mai 1987. aasta otsust 87/278/EM&Uuml; &uuml;henduse rahalise toetuse kohta seire- ja kontrollivahendite arendamiseks, mis on vajalikud &uuml;henduse korra rakendamisel kalavarude kaitseks, (1) eelk&otilde;ige selle lisa l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in accordance with Decision 87/278/EEC, the Commission has received applications for Community financial contributions; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: otsuse 87/278/EM&Uuml; kohaselt on komisjon saanud &uuml;henduse rahalise toetuse taotlusi; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the applications refer to expenditure for data processing and communication equiment, for the registration and monitoring of fishing activities and for the improvement of light sea-going craft and equipment for monitoring vessels; whereas such expenditure will help to develop monitoring and supervision facilities for the proper implementation of the Community's fishery resources conservation arrangements; </inglise>
<eesti> taotlused h&otilde;lmavad andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlus- ja andmesidevahenditele, p&uuml;&uuml;gitegevuse registreerimisele ja j&auml;relevalvele ning kergete meres&otilde;iduvahendite parandamisele ja seirelaevade seadmetele tehtavaid kulutusi; need kulutused aitavad arendada seire- ja kontrolliseadmeid &uuml;henduse kalavarude kaitse korra n&otilde;uetekohaseks rakendamiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas some of the expenditure planned is not eligible since it refers to the equipment of monitoring vessels for operation in areas not now subject to the Community's resources conservation arrangements, </inglise>
<eesti> m&otilde;ned kavandatud kulutused ei ole abik&otilde;lblikud, sest need h&otilde;lmavad seirelaevade seadmeid, mida kasutatakse tegevuseks aladel, mille suhtes praegu &uuml;henduse kalavarude kaitse korda ei kohaldata, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS DECISION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA OTSUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The expenditure shown in the Annex, in an amount of 11 013 047 ECU, is eligible for a financial contribution under Decision 87/278/EEC. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisas nimetatud kulutused summas 11 013 047 ek&uuml;&uuml;d on otsuse 87/278/EM&Uuml; alusel &uuml;henduse rahaliseks toetuseks k&otilde;lblikud. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision is addressed to the Kingdom of Denmark, the Kingdom of Spain, the French Republic, Ireland, the Kingdom of the Netherlands, the Portuguese Republic and the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev otsus on adresseeritud Taani Kuningriigile, Hispaania Kuningriigile, Iirimaale, Madalmaade Kuningriigile, Portugali Vabariigile ning Suurbritannia ja P&otilde;hja-Iiri &Uuml;hendkuningriigile. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 2 May 1988. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 2. mai 1988 </eesti>
<inglise> For the Commission Antonio CARDOSO E CUNHA Member of the Commission </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni nimel komisjoni liige Antonio CARDOSO E CUNHA </eesti>
